                    <p>The spa town of Bad Ischl is one of the largest towns in the region which you'll likely stop in
                        on your way to Hallstatt. If you have some time here you should walk around the <strong>Kongress
                            &amp; Theaterhaus</strong> to admire this elegant structure from outside, and also visit
                        the <strong>Kaiservilla</strong>, a quaint but lavish royal summer villa.</p>
                </section>



