                        (Car&nbsp;Recommended)</h2>
                    <p>Other gorgeous towns with captivating architecture and stunning scenery you might consider
                        exploring are <strong>Mondsee</strong> and <strong>St. Gilgen</strong>, both of which located
                        along the route between Salzburg and Hallstatt.</p>
                    <p>St. Gilgen is located along the western edge of Wolfgangsee, while the town of Mondsee is located
                        just to the north along the Mondsee Lake.</p>
                </section>


